{
  "_note": "LIVE APPLY - formula-backed pre-clamp plan for healing. Test target: Agrias -> Ramza healing preview/action. Formula is heal = min(missing HP, attacker.MA * 10 + target.Faith). With current Agrias/Ramza stats this should be about +210 HP, distinct from the natural +86 HP. Data mod can stay disabled. Do not use this as a balance profile; it is a narrow RE/test profile.",

  "RewriteObservedDamage": false,
